snippet.title: SEA Games 33 Thailand | Women's MLBB Knockout Stage | Bahasa Indonesia
snippet.description:
Babak Knockout Women MLBB Sea Games ke-33 Bangkok, Thailand telah tiba! 8 tim terbaik sudah ditemukan dan akan bertarung untuk merebutkan gelar juara. Persaingan pada top 8 akan semakin sulit dan semua tim akan memberikan performa terbaik mereka untuk negara tercinta. Pertarungan akan mencapai titik puncak, jangan sampai ketinggalan live nya di YouTube, Facebook, dan TikTok MLBB Esports!
#seatheglory #33rdseagames #mlbbesports

snippet.title: BARDOLO FEAT IVA JENIVA - SANDAL JEPIT ( Official Video Music )
snippet.description:
SBR PRO Mempersembahkan
Official Music Video: Bardolo Feat Iva Jeniva  - Sandal Jepit
Subscribe SBR PRO Sekarang Juga di : https://smarturl.it/SubscribeSBRPRO

Title : Sandal Jepit
Voc :  Bardolo Feat Iva Jeniva 
Song write: Andik Sugiono
Arr : Amp MUsic
Video : Nar Multimedia
Lokasi:

    "  Lirik Lagu Sandal Jepit "


L )Dik aku arep takon
Opo kowe wis ono sing duwe
Aku pengen kenalan
Karo kowe cah ayu
Sopo ngerti biso dadi bojoku

P ) Mas ngene tak kandani
Aku iki rondo anak siji
Aku ditinggal bojo
Lungo ning luar negri
Bareng bali aku di emohi

Reff.

L)Sandal jepit rupane biru
Soal duwit aku ora mampu
Tapi tentang urusan cinta
Aku iki sing paling setia

P)Sandal jepit rupane biru
Soal duwit iku nomer pitu
Yen pancene tenanan karo aku
Ndang maturo marang wong tuwoku

L&P) Yen wis podo setuju
Ayo budal bareng nyang penghulu

snippet.title: Avengers: Doomsday - First Trailer (2026) Chris Evans, Robert Downey Jr | Marvel Studios
snippet.description:
— Attention Viewers ⚠️
— This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
— robert downey jr

— This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

— In this concept trailer for Avengers: Doomsday, Avengers: Doomsday positions itself as the opening act of the Multiverse Saga’s final confrontation, where Victor von Doom rises as a master of science and sorcery who believes the multiverse must be controlled to be saved. As Earth’s heroes stand divided, Sam Wilson’s Captain America attempts to rebuild the Avengers while rival teams and uneasy alliances complicate any hope of unity. The arrival of the Fantastic Four from another reality and the long-awaited emergence of the X-Men signal that the conflict can no longer be contained within a single universe. With incursions threatening to collapse entire timelines, Doom’s ideology challenges heroes and gods alike, drawing figures like Loki into a battle over who truly holds the right to shape existence. The story frames Doomsday as a turning point where legacy, power, and sacrifice collide, setting the stage for a multiversal reckoning that will define the future of the Marvel universe.

snippet.title: Disclosure Day | Official Teaser
snippet.description:
A film by Steven Spielberg. Disclosure Day is in theaters 06.12.26.

If you found out we weren’t alone, if someone showed you, proved it to you, would that frighten you? This summer, the truth belongs to seven billion people. 
We are coming close to … Disclosure Day. 

Universal Pictures is proud to release a new original event film created and directed by Steven Spielberg. The film stars SAG winner and Oscar® nominee Emily Blunt (Oppenheimer, A Quiet Place), Emmy and Golden Globe winner Josh O’Connor (Challengers, The Crown), Oscar® winner Colin Firth (The King’s Speech, Kingsman franchise), Eve Hewson (Bad Sisters, The Perfect Couple) and two-time Oscar® nominee Colman Domingo (Sing Sing, Rustin).
 
Based on a story by Spielberg, the screenplay is by David Koepp, whose previous work with Spielberg includes the scripts for Jurassic Park, The Lost World: Jurassic Park, War of the Worlds and Indiana Jones and the Kingdom of the Crystal Skull. Combined, those films earned more than $3 billion worldwide. Koepp also wrote the script for this 2025’s Jurassic World Rebirth. 

Disclosure Day is produced by five-time Academy Award® nominee Kristie Macosko Krieger (The Fabelmans, West Side Story) and by Spielberg for Amblin Entertainment. The executive producers are Adam Somner and Chris Brigham. 

Steven Spielberg is one of the industry’s most successful and influential filmmakers. The top-grossing director of all time, Spielberg has helmed such blockbusters as Jaws, E.T. The Extra-Terrestrial, the Indiana Jones franchise and Jurassic Park. 
 
Among his myriad honors, he is a three-time Academy Award® winner, including Oscars® for Best Director and Best Picture for Schindler’s List, which received a total of seven Oscars®, and for Best Director for Saving Private Ryan. His most recent film, The Fabelmans, was released by Universal in 2022 and received seven Academy Award® nominations, including for Directing, Best Original Screenplay, Best Actress and Best Picture.

snippet.title: ALAMAK!! Survival 101 Hari di Perahu Rakit & Lawan Kraken Boss Ganas 🦑🚣‍♀️💀 | Raft 101 Indonesia
snippet.description:
ALAMAK!! Survival 101 Hari di Perahu Rakit & Lawan Kraken Boss Ganas 🦑🚣‍♀️💀 | Raft 101 Indonesia

Nama Game : Raft 101
Link Game : https://www.roblox.com/games/74256669508761

🔰 Sekarang kalau mau record, bang Hayo kabarin lewat VOICE di Room Santuy yang ada di Discord. Jadwal ga tentu, tapi biasanya kalau sore sekitar jam 15.30 - 16.30 WIB. Baca lagi bagian bawah biar kalian benar-benar mengerti 🗿

Sebelum JOIN, tolong baca ini ya 🙏😁
✅ Izin sama orang tua & tanya boleh ga install dan main Discord? Btw, discord punya aturan kalau mau buat akun mesti umur 13+
✅ PENTING!! Ikut MABAR atau RECORD mungkin agak susah karena ramai yang tungguin bang Hayo, sedangkan game Roblox server-nya terbatas
✅ Record juga GA SELALU MABAR  karena beberapa game ga boleh rusuh & mesti diatur sebaik mungkin
✅ Kalau mau record, bang Hayo kabarin lewat voice "Room Santuy" di discord
✅ Ga bisa ADD karena sudah full. Satu-satunya solusi adalah FOLLOW akun Roblox bang Hayo dan nanti kalian bisa JOIN bang Hayo main. Lalu, kalau bang Hayo lagi AFK atau SERVER sudah penuh, teman-teman ga bisa join ya
✅ Kadang bang Hayo harus pakai LINK PRIVATE SERVER biar record-nya lebih lancar. Kirim link-nya di Discord & untuk cara JOIN baca di cara-ikut-record yang ada di Discord
✅ Baca PERATURAN GROUP & PERTANYAAN UMUM  di Discord untuk kepentingan bersama
✅ Di group ini kalian juga bisa mencari KAWAN yang mungkin cocok sama kalian dan bisa main bareng. Ga perlu fokus sama bang Hayo saja karena bang Hayo ga mampu standby 24 jam
✅ Mohon pengertiannya kalau ga berhasil JOIN bang Hayo karena server sudah FULL & sistemnya siapa cepat dia masuk dulu

🔰 Bang, kenapa ga bisa chat di Discord?
Untuk menjadi MEMBER di Discord, teman-teman harus tulis username Roblox yang AKTIF di nama-roblox & baca bagian peraturan-server

🔰 Bang, CARA JOIN gimana ya?
Bang Hayo sudah jelasin secara lengkap di Discord. Cari saja di channel cara-ikut-record biar kalian paham. Lalu, akun yang umurnya kurang dari 13 tahun akan agak sulit buat join karena peraturan terbaru Roblox
